    "description": {
      "zh": "9.3x64 毫米民用 FMJ 弹药，配有重 17.5 克的全金属被甲弹头，外层被甲有助于减少弹头命中目标后发生的形变。该款弹药常用于运动射击、训练以及枪械校准，在需要减少对猎物附带损伤的打猎活动中也偶有应用。",
      "en": "A civilian 9.3x64mm Full Metal Jacket cartridge loaded with a 17.5 gram fully jacketed bullet. The full metal jacket reduces deformation on impact. This cartridge is most commonly used for sport shooting, training, and zeroing, and is sometimes used for hunting when minimal damage to game is desired."
    },
